\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk from what i can tell i think im never going to be able to run ksp2 which hurts. I use the nvidia gtx 1070ti which if the op is correct im well below spec which stinks. Can someone confirm this as i know the tweaked spec but cant locate the new. My heart says im screwed tho.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe developers have basically said that minimum requirements\u00A0 are for the initial release of early access.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerformance will improve throughout early access. There have already been improvements with the first 2 patches.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-17T01:02:16Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2023 01:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-17T01:36:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224273702\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212083\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221681690489\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk from what i can tell i think im never going to be able to run ksp2 which hurts. I use the nvidia gtx 1070ti which if the op is correct im well below spec which stinks. Can someone confirm this as i know the tweaked spec but cant locate the new. My heart says im screwed tho.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n191404162023\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe 1070ti is equaled to the minimum, not well below it. Not sure where you got that from? Unless you mean well below the recommended specs, in which case yes, but that is pretty much everyone so don\u0027t feel too bad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-17T01:37:03Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2023 01:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by MechBFP\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-17T02:14:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/184845-mechbfp/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022184845\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/184845-mechbfp/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MechBFP\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0was just going by the rtx and the 2070 and just kinda let the momentum of my personal lifes dumpster fire do the rest, but your reply gives me hope so thank you!\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nthank you as well \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161238-anth12/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161238\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161238-anth12/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Anth12\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thank you both!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n211404162023\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kojot","CreatedById":191077,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-17T06:02:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am using GTX 1060 6GB and it is playable for small